questionvariables.text:
a: rand_with_step(1,4,1);
b: a+rand_with_step(2,4,1);
c: a+1;
loes1: (a+4*c-3*b)/13;
loes2: (5*b-6*a+2*c)/13;
loes3: (4*b+3*a-c)/13;

